data.eml:eml: Report on freshwater Catenulida (Platyhelminthes) from Sweden with the description of four new species

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Larsson, Karolina, Willems, Wim (2010): Report on freshwater Catenulida (Platyhelminthes) from Sweden with the description of four new species. Zootaxa 2396: 1-18, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.193965
